sentences: Begum Parveen Sultana (Assamese: বেগম পাৰৱীন চুলতানা; born May 1950) is an Indian Hindustani classical singer of the Patiala Gharana.
Recently, she sang the theme song of Vikram Bhatt's 1920.
She also sang Humein Tumse Pyaar Kitna for the film Kudrat in 1981.
Sangeet Samraggi conferred by the Assam Government, 1994
Srimant Sankardev award by the Assam government
